Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.75,0:00:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尤莉丝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:42.87,0:00:46.10,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,just keep on trying, keep on flying\N{\c&HFFBF00&}just keep on trying, keep on flying
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.17,0:00:49.76,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be the light\N{\c&HFFBF00&}I will be the light
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.84,0:00:57.04,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果说把黎明　当作是一个开始\N{\c&HFFBF00&}夜明けをひと　つの始まりとするなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.11,0:01:04.04,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果说现在就是来临的时刻\N{\c&HFFBF00&}今が来るべき時だとするなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.12,0:01:08.65,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,与你的烟云时代交响曲\N{\c&HFFBF00&}君とのCloud Age Symphony
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.73,0:01:18.03,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,飞向云海的彼端　飞往光芒照射的方向\N{\c&HFFBF00&}雲の海の向こうに　光が射す方へ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.64,0:01:33.00,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah～是否可以遇见有如魔法的那一刻？\N{\c&HFFBF00&}Ah～魔法のような一瞬に会えるのか？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.08,0:01:40.29,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,取代寒冷的黑夜\N{\c&HFFBF00&}冷たい夜を引き替えに
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.36,0:01:47.39,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,我俩展翅飞翔\N{\c&HFFBF00&}二人は羽ばたいて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.46,0:01:58.34,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,在那尽头  抓住了永恒…\N{\c&HFFBF00&}永远を掴む、その果てには
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.46,0:02:14.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H8dccf0&}拉薇练习曲\NEtude Lavie
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.92,0:03:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是特别的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.95,0:03:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要买三级水看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.89,0:03:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三级水！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.22,0:03:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也可以喝吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.89,0:03:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.56,0:03:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大叔，给我半加仑的三级水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.90,0:03:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.96,0:03:26.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小妹妹，今晚你可有口福了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.34,0:03:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是我的生日呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.14,0:03:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我给你打个折吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.51,0:03:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.04,0:03:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.28,0:03:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.41,0:03:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇，好棒的熏肉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.71,0:03:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天保证让你肚子饱到睡不着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.35,0:03:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士的爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.02,0:03:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是个因为热爱自由的天空\N而下到这片土地来的另类贵族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.09,0:03:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自从克劳士他家\N搬到我家隔壁后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.46,0:03:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,两家父亲很快就结为好友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.90,0:04:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不久便成了一对\N先锋艇驾驶员及领航员的搭档
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.87,0:04:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和克劳士两个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.21,0:04:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,于是从一岁的时候起\N就一直在一块儿长大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.85,0:04:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的生日\N和妈妈的忌日是同一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.45,0:04:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈在生下我之后\N没多久就过世了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.69,0:04:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉就快烤好了唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.96,0:04:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士，这个就拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.13,0:04:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.70,0:04:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士他妈妈\N总是温柔地在旁看着我和爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.54,0:04:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，要拍了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.01,0:04:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.97,0:04:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.58,0:04:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我从来没有见过\N我妈妈长什么样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.32,0:04:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是我家也有照相机的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.92,0:04:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就可以留下妈妈的照片了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.96,0:05:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我完成一颗星的任务了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.10,0:05:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，辛苦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.57,0:05:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接着是下一个任务
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.71,0:05:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去妈妈那里要两杯冷饮过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.58,0:05:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危险度两颗星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.71,0:05:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暸解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.62,0:05:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你啰，克劳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.59,0:05:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇怎么在摸鱼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.23,0:05:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然接下了任务\N就得把它做完才行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.73,0:05:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人家我讨厌打扫嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.96,0:05:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把你的任务让给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.80,0:05:39.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.20,0:05:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，快还我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.07,0:05:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.07,0:05:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.64,0:05:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英麦曼式回转
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.74,0:05:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.78,0:05:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是用来测克劳地亚的压力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.21,0:05:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飞行中要目不转晴的\N好好盯着它看哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.79,0:05:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那这个呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.02,0:06:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是高度和速度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.02,0:06:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,懂了吗，再试一次看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.06,0:06:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这时机一定要抓准才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.00,0:06:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.97,0:06:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样我们就能飞了唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.58,0:06:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这还真叫人期待啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.22,0:06:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我们走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.82,0:06:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.32,0:06:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我忘了那是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.92,0:06:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一对老是跟着爸爸他们的\N大哥哥大姊姊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.96,0:06:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们到底是谁啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.00,0:06:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.01,0:06:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是护身符
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.68,0:06:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要飞越大风暴区！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.31,0:07:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要我们能把这封信\N带给度西斯的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.65,0:07:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就可以结束这场战争\N让大家过和平的日子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.32,0:07:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么了不起的任务
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.26,0:07:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然只有爸爸我们\N才能办得到啰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.53,0:07:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.09,0:07:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一颗，两颗，三颗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.53,0:07:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有十颗星耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.23,0:07:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.20,0:07:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.00,0:07:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.50,0:07:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天你也会飞上这片蓝天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.51,0:07:30.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飞得比谁都高，比谁都远
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.11,0:07:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到时候克劳士你的领航员\N说好就是拉薇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.32,0:07:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.35,0:07:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是个乖孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.82,0:07:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定可以成为\N世界第一的领航员的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.06,0:07:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸，很痛耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.56,0:07:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀，抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.73,0:07:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士，妈妈就拜托你照顾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.14,0:07:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,优蒂娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.44,0:07:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要当心点啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.28,0:08:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸，一路顺风哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.32,0:08:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一路顺风
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.18,0:08:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回来以后要再让我坐先锋艇唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.63,0:08:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒哦，是英麦曼式回转
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.97,0:08:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是我们最后一次见到爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.54,0:08:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听到爸爸他们死讯的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.85,0:08:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当时的天空好蓝好高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.29,0:08:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那位大哥哥独自一个人\N来传达这个消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.15,0:08:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后静静地回去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.49,0:08:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那也是我们最后一次\N见到那位大哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.40,0:09:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,半年后\N克劳士的妈妈积劳成疾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.07,0:09:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随他爸爸之后也过世了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.77,0:09:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从此我们变得举目无亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.71,0:09:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等将来有一天\N我们一起来飞越它
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.96,0:10:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.41,0:10:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英麦曼式回转
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.41,0:10:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惜没人在看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.68,0:10:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英麦曼他在看呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.38,0:10:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.53,0:10:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在干嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.00,0:10:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想快一点飞起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.74,0:10:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.57,0:10:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了能够飞越大风暴区
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.28,0:10:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我来当你的领航员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.52,0:11:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，克劳地亚压…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.44,0:11:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇，你还好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.12,0:11:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,节流阀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.59,0:11:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要掉下去了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.44,0:11:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…我们要飞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.90,0:12:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.87,0:12:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士，快一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.36,0:12:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飞起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.42,0:12:43.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了，克劳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.83,0:12:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在飞呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.48,0:13:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们卖掉了房子\N保住了爸爸他们的先锋艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.86,0:13:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们正在飞哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.63,0:13:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊，在飞呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.57,0:13:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.64,0:13:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.67,0:13:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士，你想干嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.71,0:13:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要去上边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.81,0:13:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去大风暴区
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.79,0:13:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士，这太乱来了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.39,0:14:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪可能这么简单\N就赶得上爸爸他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.80,0:14:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油吧，慢慢来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.85,0:14:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最后我们终于\N连住的地方都没了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.38,0:14:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我们一点都不以为苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.29,0:14:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我们\N已经可以飞翔在天空了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.59,0:14:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉上只要两人同心协力\N就没有什么做不到的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.68,0:15:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那架飞得太低了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.18,0:15:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是沃卡他儿子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.18,0:15:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，都已经到了\N可以接任务的年纪了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.42,0:15:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士，高一点，再高一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.36,0:15:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你白痴啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.65,0:15:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.66,0:16:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.47,0:16:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿到了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.50,0:16:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.80,0:16:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士，拿到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.42,0:16:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.32,0:16:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.32,0:16:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.36,0:16:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.63,0:16:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只差一点了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.99,0:17:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.84,0:17:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接着是下一个任务
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.54,0:17:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危险度两颗星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.51,0:17:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暸解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.91,0:17:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有十颗星耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.25,0:17:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.58,0:17:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,委托案第11号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.72,0:17:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,危险度三颗星，接下了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.02,0:17:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七颗星！？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.32,0:17:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七颗星耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.99,0:17:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有看过这样的任务吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.56,0:17:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是第一次看到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.93,0:17:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉很有魄力不是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.93,0:17:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎么说\N反正我还不想死啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.75,0:18:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为它是我们的先锋艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.79,0:18:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是跟你说了是直角吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.86,0:18:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真有你的，克劳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.97,0:18:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想再搭乘\N战斗用的先锋艇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.21,0:18:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士你和我所看的天空\N彼此已经不一样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.62,0:18:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以说你用来战斗的先锋艇\N就让我来负责照顾吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.05,0:18:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要成为克劳士你的机械师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.86,0:18:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要有拉薇你帮我照顾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.66,0:18:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就能放心的飞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.06,0:18:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要留在银之战舰上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.87,0:19:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士，老实说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.47,0:19:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我并不想留在银之战舰上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.34,0:19:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想和克劳士你一起\N飞在爸爸他们的蓝天上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.81,0:19:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飞得比谁都高，比谁都远
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.23,0:19:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士，你看那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.86,0:19:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.28,0:19:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天空原来是这么的壮观
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.38,0:19:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸，感觉好棒哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.56,0:19:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.63,0:20:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.44,0:20:14.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,认得出来吗，是我啦\N莫蓝．谢兰度啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.31,0:20:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,记得那个生还章吗\N你亲手作的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.74,0:20:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.95,0:20:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.32,0:20:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.82,0:20:32.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他还没回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.61,0:20:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.41,0:20:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,度西斯的移民舱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.32,0:21:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一点钟方向下方有着陆痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.79,0:21:04.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英麦曼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.16,0:21:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.23,0:21:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.74,0:21:20.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇，我端热汤过来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.44,0:21:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.15,0:21:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我得在克劳士回来之前\N把爸爸的先锋艇修好才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.59,0:21:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.39,0:21:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.56,0:21:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.07,0:21:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,借我一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.30,0:21:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里需要一点窍门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.31,0:21:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇，克劳士他回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.61,0:22:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你回来啦，克劳士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.06,0:22:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.43,0:22:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们的城镇…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.33,0:22:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诺齐亚…沦陷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.45,0:22:39.61,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,黑夜的时光逐渐逼近\N{\c&HFFBF00&}夜の時間が迫り来る
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.22,0:22:46.28,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你离我如此接近感觉  却好远…\N{\c&HFFBF00&}あなたはこんな近く  でも遠い…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.36,0:22:57.43,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你的憧憬是什么  心中想的又是誰\N{\c&HFFBF00&}何に憧れて だれを想うのか
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.50,0:23:03.03,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你舍命奋斗的身影\N{\c&HFFBF00&}いのち賭ける姿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.11,0:23:11.81,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,有一种透明的美丽  令我不禁哑口无言\N{\c&HFFBF00&}透き通る美しさに 言葉を飲んだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.89,0:23:17.76,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你欲飞往天际\N{\c&HFFBF00&}あなたが空を行くなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.82,0:23:23.56,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,我愿成为你的翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}わたしは翼になりたい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.63,0:23:29.43,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,无论风有多么强\N{\c&HFFBF00&}どんなに強い風にも
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.50,0:23:35.20,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,也永远不会折断的柔婉翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}けして折れない しなやかな羽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.28,0:23:47.24,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,相信有一天  我会拥有那样一对翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}いつか　きっと持つから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.76,0:23:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(下回预告)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.06,0:23:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然他人很温柔\N不过你别因这件衣服而想太多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.13,0:23:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有办法控制自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.70,0:23:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜穿着\N克劳士衣服的身影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.93,0:24:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是一直在我脑海挥之不去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.70,0:24:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我从没想过\N自己竟然是如此脆弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:05.87,0:24:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克劳士，你人真的很温柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.21,0:24:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一回，最后流亡 第15话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.05,0:24:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身不由己\NFairy chess
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.08,0:24:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了…苏菲亚公主
